➜iPhone 拍照「掉队」了吗？
https://www.ifanr.com/1369115?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	10015
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369124" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone1-1.png" alt="" width="1694" height="1102" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone1-1.png 1694w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone1-1-360x234.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone1-1-768x500.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone1-1-1024x666.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1694px) 100vw, 1694px" /></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369119" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_1856.jpg" alt="" width="1536" height="2048" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_1856.jpg 1536w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_1856-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_1856-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px" /></p>
<p>如果不告诉你，你可能怎么也想不到，这照片是 iPhone 4 拍的。</p>
<p>看到这张照片，很多人惊呼，过了这么多年，iPhone 4 的拍照「还是这么能打」。</p>
<p>从 iPhone 4 开始，iPhone 出色的拍照就吸引了不少用户，<strong>白平衡准确、色彩还原性好、宽容度高</strong>这三点基本是喜爱者公认的优点，拍照时流畅的体验和出色的屏幕显示效果也给摄影综合体验加分不少。</p>
<p>不过，随着国产手机厂商在摄影方面的发力，iPhone 拍照「掉队了」的说法渐渐冒头，<strong>部分国产手机用户甚至给同年度的旗舰 iPhone 的摄影水平打上了「差评」</strong>。</p>
<p>下一代全新 iPhone 发布在即，我们想讨论一个注定了作者会被「集中火力」的话题：iPhone 拍照掉队了吗？</p>
<h3><strong>iPhone 拍照进化史</strong></h3>
<p>我把 iPhone 的发展分为四个阶段，iPhone &#8211; iPhone 3GS，iPhone 4 &#8211; iPhone 6，iPhone 7 &#8211; iPhone Xs，iPhone 11 &#8211; 现在。</p>
<p><strong>1.iPhone 3GS</strong></p>
<p><strong>iPhone 3GS 的摄像头像素为 300 万</strong>，这之前的 iPhone 在拍摄方面，和当年的「老大」诺基亚暂时还拉不开多大的差距。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369129" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone3.png" alt="" width="1592" height="1192" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone3.png 1592w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone3-360x270.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone3-768x575.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone3-1024x767.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1592px) 100vw, 1592px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 像素具有浓浓的年代风. 图片来自：中关村在线</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369130" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone4.png" alt="" width="1592" height="1188" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone4.png 1592w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone4-360x269.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone4-768x573.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone4-1024x764.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1592px) 100vw, 1592px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 宽容度较低. 图片来自：中关村在线</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369131" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone5.png" alt="" width="1590" height="1186" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone5.png 1590w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone5-360x269.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone5-768x573.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone5-1024x764.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1590px) 100vw, 1590px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 细节不够丰富. 图片来自：中关村在线</p>
</div>
<p><strong>2.iPhone 4 &#8211; iPhone 6</strong></p>
<p>这一阶段最具代表性的提升是 iPhone 4，后续机型在拍照方面的进步基本都建立在 4 代的创新基础上。</p>
<p><strong>iPhone 4 当时采用了 500 万像素摄像头，1/3.2 英寸背照式 CMOS 传感器。</strong></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369154" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/251544ada221b5f820def75393bf0132.jpg" alt="" width="2592" height="1936" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/251544ada221b5f820def75393bf0132.jpg 2592w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/251544ada221b5f820def75393bf0132-360x269.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/251544ada221b5f820def75393bf0132-768x574.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/251544ada221b5f820def75393bf0132-1024x765.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2592px) 100vw, 2592px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲  iPhone 4 拍摄，良好的色彩表现</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369155" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/e033cf20686b8c881fce66223e6a4c06.jpg" alt="" width="2592" height="1936" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/e033cf20686b8c881fce66223e6a4c06.jpg 2592w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/e033cf20686b8c881fce66223e6a4c06-360x269.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/e033cf20686b8c881fce66223e6a4c06-768x574.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/e033cf20686b8c881fce66223e6a4c06-1024x765.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2592px) 100vw, 2592px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 4 拍摄，良好的虚化效果</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369156" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/85884cd96140cf4cf29bad56b9f0f35b.jpg" alt="" width="2592" height="1936" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/85884cd96140cf4cf29bad56b9f0f35b.jpg 2592w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/85884cd96140cf4cf29bad56b9f0f35b-360x269.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/85884cd96140cf4cf29bad56b9f0f35b-768x574.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/85884cd96140cf4cf29bad56b9f0f35b-1024x765.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2592px) 100vw, 2592px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 4 拍摄，良好的细节表现</p>
</div>
<p>当年，这颗传感器被媒体称作「目前为止最为先进的小型 CMOS 传感器」，其感光能力是过去同尺寸 CMOS 传感器的两倍，「因此在光线不足的环境下拍摄，理论上能够大幅降低噪点，获得更清晰的图像」。</p>
<p>再加上 iOS 4.1 加入的 <strong>HDR 算法</strong>，还有 <strong>Retina 屏幕</strong>的加持，iPhone 4 的摄影口碑在当年空前「炸裂」，优势延续了好几代产品。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369152" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0681.jpg" alt="" width="3264" height="2448" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0681.jpg 3264w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0681-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0681-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0681-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3264px) 100vw, 3264px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 5s 拍摄，使用相册 app 裁剪</p>
</div>
<p>下图请横屏观看。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369213" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0682-1.jpg" alt="" width="2442" height="9252" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0682-1.jpg 2442w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0682-1-360x1364.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0682-1-768x2910.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0682-1-270x1024.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 2442px) 100vw, 2442px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 5s 拍摄，即使到现在，仍有许多手机无法拍出宽容度和色彩表现如此优秀的全景照片</p>
</div>
<p><strong>3.iPhone 7 &#8211; iPhone Xs</strong></p>
<p>到了这个阶段，iPhone 开启了双摄时代，加入了一颗<strong>长焦镜头</strong>，用于模拟单反相机景深效果。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369135" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone6.jpg" alt="" width="3024" height="4032" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone6.jpg 3024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone6-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone6-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 3024px) 100vw, 3024px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 7 Plus 人像模式拍摄，使用相册 app 后期编辑</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369141" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone10.jpg" alt="" width="3024" height="4032" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone10.jpg 3024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone10-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone10-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 3024px) 100vw, 3024px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 7 Plus 人像模式拍摄，使用相册 app 后期编辑</p>
</div>
<p>像素方面也做了升级，从 iPhone 6 的 800 万像素，<strong>提升为 1200 万像素</strong>。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369138" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone8.jpg" alt="" width="3664" height="6516" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone8.jpg 3664w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone8-360x640.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone8-768x1366.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone8-576x1024.jpg 576w" sizes="(max-width: 3664px) 100vw, 3664px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 7 Plus 拍摄，准确记录当时的真实色彩</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369139" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone9.jpg" alt="" width="3888" height="2916" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone9.jpg 3888w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone9-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone9-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone9-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3888px) 100vw, 3888px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 7 Plus 拍摄，精准的白平衡和色彩饱和度，极好的宽容度</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369140" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone11.jpg" alt="" width="4032" height="3024" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone11.jpg 4032w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone11-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone11-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone11-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4032px) 100vw, 4032px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 7 Plus 拍摄，极好的色彩表现</p>
</div>
<p>值得注意的是，随着 iPhone X 的发布，<strong>机器学习成了 iPhone 摄影能力提升的重要一环</strong>，随后引得不少手机厂商纷纷效仿。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369143" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone13.jpg" alt="" width="2926" height="3901" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone13.jpg 2926w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone13-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone13-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 2926px) 100vw, 2926px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone Xs Max 拍摄，精准真实记录浪花拍岸瞬间</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369144" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone14.jpg" alt="" width="4032" height="3024" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone14.jpg 4032w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone14-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone14-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone14-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4032px) 100vw, 4032px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone Xs Max 拍摄，杭州西湖，出色而真实的水面波光效果</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369148" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone15.png" alt="" width="1074" height="1430" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone15.png 1074w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone15-360x479.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone15-768x1023.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone15-769x1024.png 769w" sizes="(max-width: 1074px) 100vw, 1074px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone Xs Max 拍摄，景深更准确的人像模式，良好而真实的色彩表现</p>
</div>
<p><strong>4.iPhone 11 &#8211; 现在</strong></p>
<p>iPhone 11 开始，iPhone 加入了<strong>超广角摄像头</strong>，三颗摄像头的像素都是 1200 万，还上线了<strong>夜景模式</strong>。</p>
<p>这一阶段 iPhone 较为突出的亮点是新一代的<strong> Smart HDR</strong>，不少用户反馈体验效果出众，和同样主摄像头 1200 万的 iPhone Xs 相比，成片效果有了比较大的提升。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369159" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_5267.jpg" alt="" width="3024" height="4032" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_5267.jpg 3024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_5267-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_5267-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 3024px) 100vw, 3024px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 拍摄，极具张力的超广角和出色的 Smart HDR</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369193" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone19.png" alt="" width="1084" height="1446" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone19.png 1084w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone19-360x480.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone19-768x1024.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1084px) 100vw, 1084px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 夜景模式拍摄，自然的颜色渲染和丰富的细节</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369206" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0222-2.jpg" alt="" width="4025" height="2264" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0222-2.jpg 4025w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0222-2-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0222-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_0222-2-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4025px) 100vw, 4025px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 拍摄，使用相册 app 裁剪，主摄综合表现优秀</p>
</div>
<p>还有 <strong>Deep Fusion</strong> 加入，让成片的细节纹理显示更出众。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369162" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone17.png" alt="" width="1072" height="1430" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone17.png 1072w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone17-360x480.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone17-768x1024.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1072px) 100vw, 1072px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 拍摄</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369164" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_6361.jpg" alt="" width="2236" height="3975" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_6361.jpg 2236w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_6361-360x640.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_6361-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_6361-576x1024.jpg 576w" sizes="(max-width: 2236px) 100vw, 2236px" /></p>
